            <h2>Introduction</h2>
            
            <p>Dario's Bakery</p>
            
            <p>Dario’s Bakery is your neighborhood stop for warm, handcrafted bread and pastries made fresh every day. From crisp, golden loaves to buttery croissants and classic Italian-inspired sweets, everything is baked with simple ingredients and a lot of care. Whether you’re grabbing a quick espresso and a morning treat or picking up something special to share, Dario’s brings the comfort of a real bakery to every bite. </p><!--Short description of the company-->
            
            <h2>Target audience</h2>
            
            <p>The Dario’s Bakery site is used by people who want fresh bread, pastries, desserts, and coffee—mostly local residents and families, commuters or students looking for a quick breakfast, and food lovers who care about quality, plus a secondary group like office managers and event hosts who need larger orders or catering. Their main goals are to quickly find the menu and prices, confirm hours and location, and figure out the easiest way to order or contact the bakery for custom items. They visit the site to plan a stop-in, decide what to buy ahead of time, place an order for pickup, check for specials, or get details for events like cake orders and pastry boxes.</p><!-- Who are the people who use this site? -->
           
