					<p>At Dario’s Bakery, we believe the best days start with something fresh from the oven. What began as a love for traditional baking and Italian-inspired flavors has grown into a neighborhood bakery built on simple ingredients, time-honored techniques, and the joy of sharing good food. Every morning, our team mixes, folds, proofs, and bakes in small batches so each loaf, pastry, and dessert tastes as warm and welcoming as the shop itself.</p>
			  
                    <p>We’re proud to be a place where regulars feel known, newcomers feel at home, and the smell of bread makes you slow down for a moment. Whether you’re stopping in for espresso and a croissant, picking up a crusty loaf for dinner, or ordering something special for a celebration, we’re here to make it memorable. Thanks for supporting local baking—see you at the counter.</p>

